    Note: Test defense mechanisms
    Let defense_test be test_defense_mechanism_effectiveness
    
    Note: Validate security baseline
    Let baseline_test be test_security_baseline_validation
    
    Note: Test incident response
    Let incident_response_test be test_incident_response_readiness
    
    Return SecurityScanResults with:
        vulnerability_scan as vulnerability_scan_test
        penetration_test_results as penetration_test
        security_compliance_check as compliance_test
        threat_model_validation as threat_model_test
        attack_vector_analysis as attack_vector_test
        defense_mechanism_effectiveness as defense_test
        security_baseline_validation as baseline_test
